    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">БУЙРУҚ</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#2} Буйруқ қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Ходим томонидан етказилган зарарни унинг иш ҳақи </span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">тўловларидан ушлаб қолиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 207-моддаси талабларига мувофиқ:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">1.</span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Ходимнинг ушбу ташкилотдаги лавозими</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> томонидан корхона мол-мулкига эҳтиётсиз муносабатда бўлиши натижасида корхона ҳисобига </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходим томонидан етказилган зарар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> сўм миқдорида моддий зарар етказилганлиги, ушбу зарар ходимнинг ўртача ойлик иш ҳақидан ортиқ эмаслиги маълумот учун қабул қилинсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">2. </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Ходимнинг ушбу ташкилотдаги лавозими</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">га жорий йил </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#9}Ходимнинг ойлик маошидан ушлаб қолинадиган ой</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> ойи учун ойлик иш ҳақи тўлашда <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходим томонидан етказилган зарар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\"> сўм миқдоридаги маблағлар етказилган зарарни қоплаш учун ушлаб қолинсин. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">3. Бухгалтерия ходимнинг ойлик иш ҳақи тўловларидан ушлаб қолинган маблағлар тўғрисида корхона директорига ахборот тақдим этсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">4. Мазкур фармойиш ижроси юзасидан назоратни ўз зиммамда қолдираман.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 45.2px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Асос: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Меҳнат кодексининг 164-моддаси 4-банди ҳамда 207-моддаси.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 203.50138504155px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"\">{#10}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 188.21052631579px;\">\n<p>___________</p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 228.43213296399px;\">\n<p>9_________________</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
